column2:
For example, if using terminal:

curl --request POST \
  --url https://api.climatiq.io/classifications/v1/estimate \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
    "classification": {
        "classification_type": "isic4",
        "classification_code": "25",
        "source": "EXIOBASE"
    },
    "parameters": {
        "money": 25.0,
        "money_unit": "usd"
    }
}'
